<SYNC Start=3038210><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3067588><P Class=KRCC>말하지 않을게 절대로
<SYNC Start=3070105><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3074270><P Class=KRCC>이곳에서 만난 것 말야!
<SYNC Start=3077048><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3123616><P Class=KRCC>아~~호타루!
<SYNC Start=3126040><P Class=KRCC>이모!
<SYNC Start=3127468><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3127850><P Class=KRCC>어서오너라
<SYNC Start=3129455><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
